list.title: JOKE 1
list.content: I can't wait to retire so l can get up at 6 and go drive around really slowly and make everyone late for work.

list.title: JOKE 2
list.content: The most disturbing thing about accidentally waking up at 4am is realising some people do this on purpose so they can exercise.

list.title: JOKE 3
list.content:
My girlfriend dressed up as a policewoman and told me I was under arrest on suspicion of being good in bed.
After 2 minutes all charges were dropped due to a lack of evidence.

list.title: JOKE 4
list.content: I think my dog always follows me to the bathroom because I always follow him outside and he thinks that's the way it works.

list.title: JOKE 5
list.content: I think my dog always follows me to the bathroom because I always follow him outside and he thinks that's the way it works.

list.title: JOKE 6
list.content:
We do not throw away perfectly good food in this house.
We put it in Tupperware & wait for it to go bad & then we throw it away.

list.title: JOKE 7
list.content:
How to dress for cold weather:
1. Put pajamas back on
2. Get back in bed

list.title: JOKE 8
list.content: Shout out to the people who lock their front door and then have to check it three times to make sure it's locked!

list.title: JOKE 9
list.content:
I love board games. My favorite is when people put meat and cheese on a board. Maybe some crackers and fruit.
I'm really good at that one.

list.title: JOKE 10
list.content:
Sometimes I like to mess with my husband and hide his stuff where he can't find it.
Like I put his shoes in the shoe closet, his jacket on the hanger and his keys on the key hook.

list.title: JOKE 11
list.content: I posted a photo of myself at the gym, and it was flagged and removed as 'Fake News.'

list.title: JOKE 12
list.content: I'm so old I remember when cars had bench seats and no seatbelts — and we thought that was normal!

list.title: JOKE 13
list.content: I used to think being at home and doing nothing all day was boring, but as an adult it’s literally my definition of a good day.

list.title: JOKE 14
list.content: I hate it when people ask me if I did anything exciting over the weekend... like I'm over here skydiving. I'm 50. I went to Walmart, did some laundry, ate too much food, and took a nap.

list.title: JOKE 15
list.content: You know you're getting old when a recliner and a heating pad is your idea of a hot date.

list.title: JOKE 16
list.content: The best way to save money is to go in the house and lay down.

list.title: JOKE 17
list.content: Why am I the only one around here doing the dishes, paying bills, and cooking dinner? Sure, I live alone... but still…

list.title: JOKE 18
list.content: I can't decide if people who wear pajamas in public have given up on life or are living it to the fullest.

list.title: JOKE 19
list.content: At my funeral take the flowers off my coffin & throw it to the crowd so we can see who is next.

list.title: JOKE 20
list.content:
So my rum and raisin cake is gluten free.
It's also raisin free. And cake free.
OK it's just rum.

list.title: JOKE 21
list.content: My toxic trait is telling people I'm up for anything when in reality I mean not after 8 pm, food should be involved, and it also depends on the weather, the parking situation, and how tired I am.

list.title: JOKE 22
list.content: I don't care how old I get. If I'm in a store and I see a toy with 'Try me' on it, I'm pushing those buttons.

list.title: JOKE 23
list.content: When your wife starts a sentence with 'when you get a chance' just go ahead and start putting your shoes on. She means now.

list.title: JOKE 24
list.content: Lazy Confession: Sometimes I don't feel like thawing meat so I just go buy another pack instead.

list.title: JOKE 25
list.content: I just wanna apologize to the people I called old at 50 when I was 18.

list.title: JOKE 26
list.content: Everyone thinks tall people have a lot of advantages in life, but in reality, they have to deal with 40% more spider webs than the average person.

list.title: JOKE 27
list.content: If you can't look back at your younger self and realize that you were an idiot, you are probably still an idiot.

list.title: JOKE 28
list.content: I'm well on my way to getting absolutely nothing done today.

list.title: JOKE 29
list.content: I don't know how to use TikTok. But I can write in cursive and do long division. I can also tell time on clocks with hands.

list.title: JOKE 30
list.content:
Sometimes I wake up grumpy.
But other times I let her sleep in.

list.title: JOKE 31
list.content: The older I get the tighter companies are putting lids on jars.

list.title: JOKE 32
list.content:
If you ever think English is not a weird language just remember that read and lead rhyme and read and lead rhyme.
But read and lead don't rhyme, and neither do read and lead.

list.title: JOKE 33
list.content: Just saw 3 people jogging outside and it inspired me to get up and close the blinds.

list.title: JOKE 34
list.content:
Thought I'd be trendy and try one of these
'alternative milks'
I don't know what a magnesia is, but it made my cornflakes taste horrible.

list.title: JOKE 35
list.content: When a cougar gets so old she needs a hearing aid, she becomes a Def Leppard.

list.title: JOKE 36
list.content: I love putting on warm underwear fresh out of the dryer. Plus it's fun to look around the laundromat and guess who they belong to.

list.title: JOKE 37
list.content:
When you're a kid, it makes you feel proud when someone says 'Wow!
You've gotten so big since the last time I saw you!'
As an adult, not so much.

list.title: JOKE 38
list.content: I tried to use my grocery store loyalty card to scrape my windshield, but I only got 20% off.

list.title: JOKE 39
list.content:
My wife just found out I replaced our bed with a trampoline.
She hit the roof.

list.title: JOKE 40
list.content:
My girlfriend dressed up as a policewoman and told me I was under arrest on suspicion of being good in bed.
After 2 minutes all charges were dropped due to a lack of evidence.

list.title: JOKE 41
list.content:
Fun fact: Koi fish always travel in groups of 4.
If attacked koi A B and C will scatter leaving behind the D koi.

list.title: JOKE 42
list.content: I'm at the age where not finding parking for an event is enough to make me go home.

list.title: JOKE 43
list.content: Why can't dinosaurs clap their hands? Because they're extinct.

list.title: JOKE 44
list.content: I got a new pen that can write under water. It can write other words too.

list.title: JOKE 45
list.content: How did I know my girlfriend thought I was invading her privacy? She wrote about it in her diary.

list.title: JOKE 46
list.content: Most women aren't looking for a man to take care of them anymore, they're just looking for a man they don't have to take care of.

list.title: JOKE 47
list.content: When scientists said the Universe is made up of protons, neutrons and electrons, they forgot to mention morons.

list.title: JOKE 48
list.content:
Getting old sucks big time.
I just threw my back out because the toaster startled me.

list.title: JOKE 49
list.content:
One day you'll find someone that's
obsessed with you.
It's probably going to be a dog but it is what it is.

list.title: JOKE 50
list.content: A telemarketer called & asked to speak to whoever runs the household. So I passed the phone to my dog.

list.title: JOKE 51
list.content: The scariest feeling in the world is the split second you lose your balance in the shower and think, OH GOD, THEY'RE GOING TO FIND ME NAKED!

list.title: JOKE 52
list.content: Sometimes the thoughts in my head get bored so they go out for a stroll through my mouth. This is rarely a good thing.

list.title: JOKE 53
list.content: You know you're getting old when you can't walk past a bathroom without thinking, 'I may as well pee while I'm here'.

list.title: JOKE 54
list.content: Finally figured out why I look so bad in pictures - it’s my face.
